                Solidus offers Goby the flexibility we need to meet our ever-growing business demands. The ability to fully customize our site has been a meaningful driver of the continued growth of our business.
              </p>
            </div>
            <footer class="blockquote-footer pt-3">
              <cite>
                <img src="<%= image_path("quotes/ben-goldberg.png") %>" data-srcset="<%= image_path("quotes/ben-goldberg@2x.png") %> 2x, <%= image_path("quotes/ben-goldberg.png") %> 1x" class="img-circled" width="48" height="48" alt="Ben Goldberg" />
